quote><br />\n明白，想問下巴打有無考慮返香港返工？<br />\n如果想返日資公司，拎個n1係咪會著數好多？</blockquote><br />\n我覺得入日資公司重要係你敬語講得好<br />\n太多香港人有N1, 其實無咩用</blockquote><br />\n咁其實係咪如果唔係日本返工既話基本上無咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161f757ca298b4020f8fdd2a9063d70ec68f0f45","tid":142450,"uid":26963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T17:07:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9abeb5fecd587e072e1a102191c20b276cf931b8","tid":142450,"uid":26963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T17:24:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b345ac2efa981b9ffffc223142aa9f4c155b1519","tid":142450,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T20:25:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係日本混左半年拎左個n1<br />\n而家去左日本做野<br />\n<br />\n其實你只要拎到n1就得無人理你係邊度讀<br />\n不過當然係日本讀會快啲<br />\n但你唔好諗住淨係靠學校<br />\n讀日本你係香港都搵到日文老師</blockquote><br />\n <br />\nmore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀咩?點搵野做?</blockquote><br />\n我都想more啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返來啦皮卡秋巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想知點樣咁快上到N1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30924984ffd9183035e37ce6d077d0c2e3f6f22","tid":142450,"uid":25882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T21:21:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係日本混左半年拎左個n1<br />\n而家去左日本做野<br />\n<br />\n其實你只要拎到n1就得無人理你係邊度讀<br />\n不過當然係日本讀會快啲<br />\n但你唔好諗住淨係靠學校<br />\n讀日本你係香港都搵到日文老師</blockquote><br />\n <br />\nmore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀咩?點搵野做?</blockquote><br />\n我都想more啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返來啦皮卡秋巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想知點樣咁快上到N1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尋晚一早訓左今朝去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身無底<br />\n啱啱去到日本個時成個遊客咁基本野都講唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比個有底friend捉左去一齊考n1<br />\n諗住反正都要考咪試下自己可以去到幾盡<br />\n個幾個月基本上書不離手<br />\n錄鐘意睇既電視不停聽同睇字幕睇學點用啲字同文法<br />\n之後就半年碌過左n1<br />\n<br />\n當然n1只係入場券<br />\n只係用黎比你interview<br />\n我係internal transfer老闆都係見我有n1先比我in<br />\n<br />\n講到敬語<br />\n其實敬語本身唔難<br />\n日本人其實自己都會用錯所以唔驚<br />\n但敬語難既地方唔係文法而係點包裝句句子<br />\n有啲似係語言偽術<br />\n但呢樣野己經唔係日文既問題你唔識既中文你都唔會識講"},{"pid":"817464b49b656e47dd49176ffaaea1ba399b4ede","tid":142450,"uid":26963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:16:46.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打講咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪只要有n1基本上日常對話同返工用都無問題？"},{"pid":"ce108bb5b503910a1dd90b5e917421e51875c7b8","tid":142450,"uid":26963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:03:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38d6cbea9c512104de9c928cba61462acaf7b843","tid":142450,"uid":62628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:55:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝巴打講咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪只要有n1基本上日常對話同返工用都無問題？</blockquote><br />\n日本學就係,香港識好多n1啞仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f05093b1bbc146651c089f866892c33e644e8d23","tid":142450,"uid":26963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:06:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>多謝巴打講咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪只要有n1基本上日常對話同返工用都無問題？</blockquote><br />\n日本學就係,香港識好多n1啞仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa