726c","tid":142450,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係日本混左半年拎左個n1<br />\n而家去左日本做野<br />\n<br />\n其實你只要拎到n1就得無人理你係邊度讀<br />\n不過當然係日本讀會快啲<br />\n但你唔好諗住淨係靠學校<br />\n讀日本你係香港都搵到日文老師</blockquote><br />\n <br />\nmore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀咩?點搵野做?</blockquote><br />\n我都想more啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返來啦皮卡秋巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想知點樣咁快上到N1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尋晚一早訓左今朝去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身無底<br />\n啱啱去到日本個時成個遊客咁基本野都講唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比個有底friend捉左去一齊考n1<br />\n諗住反正都要考咪試下自己可以去到幾盡<br />\n個幾個月基本上書不離手<br />\n錄鐘意睇既電視不停聽同睇字幕睇學點用啲字同文法<br />\n之後就半年碌過左n1<br />\n<br />\n當然n1只係入場券<br />\n只係用黎比你interview<br />\n我係internal transfer老闆都係見我有n1先比我in<br />\n<br />\n講到敬語<br />\n其實敬語本身唔難<br />\n日本人其實自己都會用錯所以唔驚<br />\n但敬語難既地方唔係文法而係點包裝句句子<br />\n有啲似係語言偽術<br />\n但呢樣野己經唔係日文既問題你唔識既中文你都唔會識講</blockquote><br />\n想知巴打你點樣搵工?"},{"pid":"7692c78c23410349b70f579c15c8d2e60406104f","tid":142450,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T15:46:15.000Z","msg":"今日報左個10星期既商業日語短期course<br />\n係大阪既TERA,希望學好d敬語"},{"pid":"b489028959e52c9d4fe6530345640cb26abf25db","tid":142450,"uid":26963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:06:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日報左個10星期既商業日語短期course<br />\n係大阪既TERA,希望學好d敬語</blockquote><br />\n巴打係諗住係香港搵工定日本？"},{"pid":"81c66a4acd73e9668e41825519e8caa6537cf675","tid":142450,"uid":1169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:41:54.000Z","msg":"黎緊報exchange<br />\nstudy plan用日文好難寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4137b1075998bb1ffbcf9340ada020020154e7","tid":142450,"uid":26963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊報exchange<br />\nstudy plan用日文好難寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加油啊巴打<br />\n我都好想去日本讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ec7995337bb4d2eeac492807fbfb80d439ce99","tid":142450,"uid":29351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T17:04:27.000Z","msg":"今日都報左三峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  10月岀發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772dac881335451fed19b153b9398815caa316d7","tid":142450,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T17:24:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日都報左三峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  10月岀發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打去讀一年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身咩學歷有無日文底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c86764514895b72635c2fbb3476a436e6f10232","tid":142450,"uid":26963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T17:31:01.000Z","msg":"想知讀完/讀緊既咁多位巴打會係日本返工定香港？"},{"pid":"b0347fced46be8c54e5b0a50e10f7d390d266e71","tid":142450,"uid":26963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T00:36:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d545ea98dfe25dccc1a731dfcd7e39106789a769","tid":142450,"uid":29351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T02:06:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今日都報左三峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  10月岀發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打去讀一年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身咩學歷有無日文底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n9月開始自學 7月應該考左n4先 n3未開始學但應該趕唔切進度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b0504ed360450f53df3858e815d22434dfc7f4","tid":142450,"uid":26963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:28:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c7a50ff77f70097de9d9c1b6e61457204f54adc","tid":142450,"uid":73419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:32:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係日本混左半年拎左個n1<br />\n而家去左日本做野<br />\n<br />\n其實你只要拎到n1就得無人理你係邊度讀 <br />\n不過當然係日本讀會快啲<br />\n但你唔好諗住淨係靠學校<br />\n讀日本你係香港都搵到日文老師</blockquote><br />\n明白，想問下巴打有無考慮返香港返工？<br />\n如果想返日資公司，拎個n1係咪會著數好多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問黎都多餘 你咁問同問如果你有n1係咪會著數過n2一樣"},{"pid":"722c521f6ad4657a9327ecfe641c3ff17d9e6357","tid":142450,"uid":8795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:43:14.000Z","msg":"打算出年4月去"},{"pid":"7c49d3b533b17b4f219f7791222d085c521d0392","tid":142450,"uid":22599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:53:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aee76b2aaeafe0d0d16e4b86710839e1779458a5","tid":142450,"uid":26963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係日本混左半年拎左個n1<br />\n而家去左日本做野<br />\n<br />\n其實你只要拎到n1就得無人理你係邊度讀 <br />\n不過當然係日本讀會快啲<br />\n但你唔好諗住淨係靠學校<br />\n讀日本你係香港都搵到日文老師</blockquote><br />\n明白，想問下巴打有無考慮返香港返工？<br />\n如果想返日資公司，拎個n1係咪會著數好多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問黎都多餘 你咁問同問如果你有n1係咪會著數過n2一樣</blockquote><br />\nSorry絲打 我都係想有多啲人覆可以解答下我啲問題 <br />\n想問下絲打是咪都有讀？"}]}